title: Justin Bieber Debuts 'Purpose' Album Artwork - See All Three Versions Here
text: Justin Bieber bows his head while shirtless in front some markings on the artwork for his upcoming album, Purpose. The 21-year-old musician debuted the official artwork for the album on Instagram, before adding three in blue, white and black.
